flotar sobre un chico.

414
00:33:23,419 --> 00:33:27,214
Era mayor que yo, y le hice señas,

415
00:33:27,297 --> 00:33:30,467
grité, intenté advertirle, pero...

416
00:33:30,551 --> 00:33:31,844
